thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Brenda Ramirez

author: Brenda Ramirez
title: Brenda Ramirez
text: Let me start with saying the customer service is amazing, it's like the old fashioned genuine caring folks that really care about getting what you need and when you need it. They go above and beyond with detail and process. Products are 100% authentic at great prices and a huge assortment to pick from. Can't wait to order again... xoxo
